{"tid":808328,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"空姐叫她「小姐」！女控航空公司性別歧視：登機證上寫博士","createTime":"2018-09-06T08:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T11:00:54.000Z","uid":4876,"like":2,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc42023fa878925c6971be21e54383f5980ffda","tid":808328,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"英國一名女博士奧德懷爾（Siobhan O'Dwyer）上個月31日搭乘澳洲航空（QANTAS），未料空姐稱她「小姐」讓她相當不滿，因此控訴航空公司性別歧視，因為登機證上明明寫著她是「奧德懷爾博士」，結果此篇貼文引起網友兩派論戰，還有人傻眼回應「會不會反應過度了」。<br />\n<br />\n英國女博士不滿空姐叫她小姐，怒告「性別歧視」。（圖／翻攝Dr Siobhan O'Dwyer推特） <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/06/165621_322c71e9037dc50fcd51fa1d249285f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F165621_322c71e9037dc50fcd51fa1d249285f9.jpg&h=99718d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲英國女博士不滿空姐叫她小姐，而非博士。（圖／翻攝Dr Siobhan O'Dwyer推特）<br />\n<br />\n奧德懷爾表示，當天她搭澳洲航空登機時，機組人員看著她登機證卻稱她「小姐」，「我的登機證上面是奧德懷爾（Dr O'Dwyer）博士」，還說自己在大學工作了8年，從來沒遇過這種事，「如果我是一個男性，這不會發生。」她認為澳航性別歧視，結果引起網友論戰，超過2千人留言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/06/165723_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F165723_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=9bc6406f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=426229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D426229&d=cDinVvufwTKkQuZWXBaguAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=69b8b519\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D426229&h=9d94fe42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=426229</a>"},{"pid":"3d36d1011943ce4d4a0bd1101f6e5774baf36a14","tid":808328,"uid":63588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"應該叫八婆"},{"pid":"300f64f856edba03d5ef015b7ac17e65afa5be